  "Description": {
    "English": "Equip this exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Personal Flair</span> in commemoration of the 'Exobiology' <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Expedition</span>, and your explorations into the diverse wildlife inhabiting the universe.<br><br>Apply this banner to your profile at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
